Titolo: Minority Report: Everybody Runs

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Minority Report: Everybody Runs is a 2002 third-person shooter beat 'em up video game based on the 2002 film Minority Report. It was developed for the PlayStation 2, GameCube, and Xbox by Treyarch, and for the Game Boy Advance by Torus Games, and published by Activision. A Microsoft Windows version of the game was also planned but cancelled.

Genere: Beat \'em up

Valutazione: 52
